author: COMSOL
description: This benchmark computes the total force acting on a vibrating disc in the frequency and time domains and compares both results with expressions derived analytically. When the vibration amplitude is small enough that the system is linear the frequency- and time-domain results agree well with theory. Larger amplitude vibrations, which result in a nonlinear response that cannot be modeled in the frequency domain, are explored in the time domain, and compared against analytic solutions.
